Personaly, Since both my parents are in the Goverment,My Dad is a Major in the Army, and hes told me certian things about that area…
What I think:
Aliens: Yes. Roswell, NM, 1946,
Aircraft: Yes,they test aircraft there also
Serect Bunker: Ohhh yah, If they don’t do the things above, it’s probaly the Presidental Bunker.

That Satilite image is the airport where the people GO to Area 51, not the place its self
They also tested Nuclear/Hygogen Bombs in that area form the late 40’s to the early 70’s and that radiation was found in both north and south poles.
Keep this in mind, On July 8, 1967, we were 14 minutes from Nuclear Armagetton
